\c 9
\s Dhavhidhi anochengeta Mefibhosheti mwanakomana waSauro
\p
\v 1 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakati: Kuchine umwe wakasara weimba yaSauro kuti ndimuitire tsitsi nekuda kwaJonatani here\x + 9.7. 10.1. 1 Sam. 18.3. 20.14,17,42.\x*?
\v 2 Zvino imba yaSauro yaiva nemuranda wezita raiva Zibha\x + 16.1-4. 19.17,29.\x*. Pavaiva vamudanira kuna Dhavhidhi, mambo ndokuti kwaari: Ndiwe Zibha here? Iye ndokuti: Muranda wenyu \add ndiye\add*.
\v 3 Zvino mambo wakati: Hakuchina munhu here weimba yaSauro, wandingaitira tsitsi dzaMwari\x + 1 Sam. 20.14.\x*? Zibha ndokuti kuna mambo: Jonatani achine mwanakomana wakaremara tsoka dziri mbiri\x + 4.4.\x*.
\v 4 Mambo ndokuti kwaari: Aripi? Zibha ndokuti kuna mambo: Tarirai, ari mumba maMakiri mwanakomana waAmieri kuRhodhebhari\x + 17.27. Josh. 13.26.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Zvino mambo Dhavhidhi wakatuma \add nhume\add* akandomutora kubva mumba maMakiri mwanakomana waAmieri kuRhodhebhari\x + 17.27. Josh. 13.26.\x*.
\v 6 Mefibhosheti mwanakomana waJonatani mwanakomana waSauro paakasvika kuna Dhavhidhi wakawa nechiso chake, ndoku\add mu\add*kotamira. Dhavhidhi ndokuti: Mefibhosheti! Iye ndokuti: Tarirai, muranda wenyu.
\p
\v 7 Dhavhidhi ndokuti kwaari: Usatya, nokuti zvirokwazvo ndichakuitira tsitsi nekuda kwaJonatani baba vako, uye ndichakudzosera nyika yose yaSauro baba vako; uye iwe uchadya chingwa patafura yangu nguva dzose\x + 9.1,3.\x*.
\v 8 Zvino iye wakakotama ndokuti: Muranda wenyu chii kuti mutarise imbwa yakafa yakaita seni\x + 16.9. 1 Sam. 24.14.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Zvino mambo wakadana Zibha muranda waSauro ndokuti kwaari: Zvose zvaiva zvaSauro nezveimba yake yose ndakazvipa mwanakomana watenzi wako.
\v 10 Zvino iwe uchamurimira ivhu, iwe nevanakomana vako nevaranda vako, uye muchaunza \add mbesa\add* kuti mwanakomana watenzi wako ave nezvekudya zvaangadya; asi Mefibhosheti mwanakomana watenzi wako achagara achidya zvekudya patafura yangu\x + 9.7,11,13. 19.28. 1 Madz. 2.7. 2 Madz. 25.29.\x*. Zvino Zibha waiva nevanakomana gumi nevashanu nevaranda makumi maviri\x + 19.17.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino Zibha wakati kuna mambo: Zvichienderana nezvose ishe wangu, mambo, zvaaraira muranda wake, muranda wenyu achaita saizvozvo. Kana ari Mefibhosheti, \add mambo anoti:\add* Achadya patafura yangu seumwe wevanakomana vamambo\x + Eki. 18.4.\x*.
\v 12 Zvino Mefibhosheti waiva nemwanakomana mudiki, zita rake raiva Mika\x + 1 Makor. 8.34.\x*. Uye umwe neumwe waiva agere mumba maZibha, vakava varanda vaMefibhosheti.
\v 13 Zvino Mefibhosheti wakagara paJerusarema, nokuti waidya patafura yamambo nguva dzose; waiva akaremara tsoka dzake dziri mbiri.